**This complainant already has a signature on file with us. Below is the
latest email request:
From: "dmca.tcg " 
Subject: 070930 To Google Re Re: [#189199675] 070820-Copyright infringement
complaint to Google regarding
Date: Sun, 30 Sep 2007 17:36:38 +[private]

Dear Google Team,

Thanks very much for your efforts in completing processing my DMCA complaint
on www.topchinatravel.com.

I have found all the infringing web pages have removed from your search
result except for four pages as follows:
http://www.topchinatravel.com/information-of-china/history_of_china.asp
http://www.topchinatravel.com/cityguide/Guilin/index.asp
http://www.topchinatravel.com/cityguide/dalian/attraction/tiger_beach_sea_pa
rk.asp
http://www.topchinatravel.com/yangtze/yangtze_sightseeing.asp

Hope you can give a further investigation.

Thanks in advance.

Sincerely,
[private]
